<!DOCTYPE ui:UiBinder SYSTEM "http://dl.google.com/gwt/DTD/xhtml.ent">
<ui:UiBinder xmlns:ui="urn:ui:com.google.gwt.uibinder"
	xmlns:g="urn:import:com.google.gwt.user.client.ui">
	
    <ui:with field='res' type='com.owb.playhelp.client.resources.Resources'/>
    
	<ui:style src="../../../resources/GlobalStyles.css">
		.important {
			font-weight: bold;
		}
		.description{
	        color:#9152a0;
	        margin: 30px;
	   }
	</ui:style>
	<g:HTMLPanel>
	   <div class="{style.description}">
	    <h1>CLEAN WATER</h1>
			<div class="{style.descwrapper}">
				<div class="{style.descpic}">
					<g:Image url='{res.waterWebPic.getSafeUri.asString}' pixelSize="300,300"/>
				</div>
				<div class="{style.desclabel}">
				Water is an essential element for life. In regions where there is a water crisis it can affect 
				other areas as education. In addition, germs in water cause diseases and death. We aim to provide
				clean water to orphan and abandoned children. We support projects aiming to bring clean water
				to the children that need it.
    		    </div>
    		    </div>
		</div>
	</g:HTMLPanel>
</ui:UiBinder> 